---
title: Sweet Chilli Prawn & Broccoli Stir-Fry with Egg Noodles
description: Prawns that are popping with delicious taste sensations, we say yes please! You won’t be able to get enough of these bad boys in a saucy sweet chilli stir-fry. Set off the flavour fireworks with ginger and oyster sauce stirred through.

*This recipe is under 650kcal per serving.*
